  "plainText": "Exclusive to:\nMeated Nettles\nNormal\nPig Fiesta\nFood Info\n37.5\n20\n5\nMeat\nObject Info\nPerk\nGrants immunity to Hayfever for 600 seconds\n8 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx2 x1 x1\n20 seconds\n1\nMiscellaneous\n\"meated_nettle\"\n“Improved with scientific meat-wrapping technology.”\n–Wilson\n“It clears my snot.”\n–Willow\n“Meaty snack clears Wolfgang's mighty nostrils!”\n–Wolfgang\n“Temporary relief for life's grief... wrapped in meat.”\n–Wendy\n“NOSE IRRITANT EJECTOR WITH MEAT ATTATCHMENT”\n–WX-78\n“Medicinal nourishment, with added protein.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“It's not back bacon, but it'll do.”\n–Woodie\n“Meaty and medicinal.”\n–Maxwell\n“Wrapping the fronds in meat makes them considerably more palatable.”\n–Wagstaff\n“This meat hath a strange texture within, but my sinuses art clear!”\n–Wigfrid\n“They're more yummy this way”\n–Webber\n“The meat helps cover the medicine smell.”\n–Walani\n“Medicinal leaves with some added flavor.”\n–Warly\n“A bite o' meat to go with th'nose clearin'!”\n–Woodlegs\n“GOODNESS FOR TH'SNOUT AND TH'BELLY”\n–Wilba\n“Mmmm...”\n–Wormwood\n“The meat helps the medicine go down.”\n–Wheeler\nThe Meated Nettles are a Food Item exclusive to Hamlet. They can be cooked in a Crock Pot with at least two Nettles and a Meat value of at least one. Filler cannot be Inedibles. Adding Honey will result in Honey Nuggets. Adding more than one Monster Food will result in Monster Lasagna.\nMeated Nettles can be eaten by the player to stave off Hay Fever for 600 seconds (1.25 Days).\nAs it is considered a Meat dish, Wigfrid can consume Meated Nettles, unlike raw Nettles or Nettle Rolls.\nContents\n1 Prerequisites\n2 Recipe\n3 Example\n4 Trivia\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires :\nRequires:\nExcludes:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\n×2\nExample[edit | edit source]\n×2\n×2\n×2\n×2\n×3\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nThe Meated Nettles were added in the March 2023 Quality of Life Beta update.\nMeated nettles allow Wigfrid to avoid hayfever without having to wear a gas mask.\nDuring the Pig Fiesta event in the Hamlet DLC, Meated Nettles take on a more festive appearance.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
